column5: Wow that one on the left is a brute.  Bring that one up to Lakair with you will ya.  That would feed us all for the week. We'll deep fry it after the fish fry

Thanks Wayne.   I twiked my mcl friday,so there was no fishing or hunting for me since Friday. Been able to huble to the BBQ an back,as I am the bbq guy here,but Betty has been just grand with the pouring.LOL
